<HI>Molo&s;&s;ian dogs</HI> of the ancients, according to Mr. Buffon, iii.
293&mdash;<HI>Epirotic dogs,</HI> mentioned by Pli|ny, iii.
295&mdash;<HI>Indian dogs,</HI> mentioned by Aelian&mdash;his de&s;cription of
a combat between a dog and a lion, iii. 295, 296&mdash;the Engli&s;h <HI>bull
dog,</HI> iii. 290&mdash;the brave&s;t of the kind&mdash;the nobler kinds of
