<ITEM><HI>Mu&s;cles,</HI> to judge of the &s;trength of animals by
the <PB REF="408"> thickne&s;s of their mu&s;cles inconclu&s;ive, ii.
120&mdash;tho&s;e of the hare are &s;trong and without fat, iv. 4&mdash;the
pectoral mu&s;cles of quadrupeds trifling in compari&s;on to tho&s;e of
