<ITEM><HI>Peacock,</HI> varieties of this bird&mdash;&s;ome white,
others <PB REF="432"> cre&s;ted&mdash;that of Thibet, the mo&s;t beautiful of
the feathered creation, v. 176&mdash;a &s;aying among the ancients, as
