<ITEM><HI>Plants</HI> and vegetables compared with animals,
&s;imili|tude&mdash;how a&s;&s;imilated in different climates and &s;oils, ii.
3 to 8&mdash;will not grow &s;o fa&s;t in di&s;tilled as undi&s;tilled water,
