<ITEM><HI>Sound</HI> conveyed by air, is lo&s;t in vacuo, i.
334.&mdash;&s;ounding bodies of two kinds; unela&s;tic returning a &s;ingle
&s;ound, and ela&s;tic rendering a &s;ucce&s;&s;ion of
&s;ounds&mdash;undulations in ela&s;tic bodies, taken by the ear as one
