&s;ide whence &s;ound comes, ii. 173&mdash;trumpets made to encrea&s;e
&s;ounds, ii. 174</ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Source,</HI> rivers have their &s;ource in mountains, or
ele|vated lakes, i. 200</ITEM>
<ITEM><HI>Southmin&s;ter</HI> mar&s;hes &s;o over-run with an army
